[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Analyzing metadata generation**\n\nI’m thinking about how tests execute the JVM with an agent to generate metadata. It’s possible that using MethodHandles for private methods doesn’t generate the necessary reflection metadata. Then, if I consider native image compilation, it might not include those private methods for MethodHandle lookup, which could lead to failures. I wonder how that all ties together and if there's a way to resolve these issues.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_093431a5b2e65008016a03252b46708194bed4997cc3acda0f\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqAyU8BvjotgXeqDMszKrPxJNJoj5iw3ZlDzAnfMcjZyCVkt6axxBPVxrh3U2AfkB37nC5caHSGy0La8yEh2wd0L0emXhioMNg37H-SuS5lFXlNC8sxn0Jl3XW80StomEM3Uqw6KU0v9eM_LtmDLeVbOdNkub8uuaHH1QydF2JyicdqwAK9oXowapt-qXUDyiRrrHjBP_yUU82QbVoe0cNSeDP-RPt7ZalMXT5Om8W2EfxlU4Hfh-3LzMz7vtpOu8VPg5xKL0v1U4yMcNYPBNzCkbl9P8WkKGuWujc0JZXOu-AFFXdzQHil_6iTpHmCqNoE2iJ1PXKihkT3wmPjwohuo5cs8nsQVsv5SqAgTyb-kSPKqh70D6FTvxUzPL0tbDAhqMP7ubpW2W8G88JpPCdf21EuY-yCDnwJrxMHBO5s6Fw-GSFIw_NXyb7peZtH9SjZDjEIUc2FXZhuuGF7_Z-g4jB2Q8KWgaihaMYmL3poZSzzxUy-fp8VUkBZ6ix0cKgLyOjkJG5DkfOlqOUXLdYqs85_S2aeh8H-_qJSKLA81bRkpimGpFKEvxU0P2fwHIU7WYjo_Qrdh4bUhTjq71i9Uq8KKwmTm0OhWBmQQb8o75in3Io_cFUDRlkvlG1-zNMLXpxMSH_qCjbAeNc1RV07FDVLGacnvmRbej2QX5fXQXjybW9NSm6plFKN6iFV3hm1fYYYEi79gXGGwVzbWJ9PGRnzMHqaidh7vLUSpXgkctk2OG2d9UMVt3Nkw3GWVab9dZ_jfR0pamiHD3mAme-d8bIqoz4f0OgRUWiOvqN39fM2HVFlKRYx-MnKFBnAHBFeQeh0n1MoNBpxZGdvcKqxcNnNAoOD7F5KMcpz5n7Ex7vs9NotQe-8C1IvfCQwCxWkRuRC5KNzqTYx5j8OxNrs7i1FTxBXK2o9e0nVsOLtpwkr4kX8Z7c8g1EWXVGoh4X41cHnrVl91WQIl4-3XLfj0xHhdSyTTK-PMKlLpikVPFR93Jcx6EA7FfY079q2vr33-fsqNdQyydhZ7axFjanyzpeQUG5gPVBjjW_fQ8jc1znvQrCgDe7jtilbLga2KH6EGYyS-f314UTbS5-b0HwFDnk6cs5j-K_Mix5bQ9PnUVIWqQcGYHZBvfnokvbHHzR5IKF_Os0GfK9HVANAH6AwzaDiWQVn9gi5-yVSEVekfPt0uQuX4HyDxmrogCyJKm-fkwVdPLMmyB1RM1M56CmQV2V7zJBIeUNKHyhViPvW0kqbH2OBslPFt-ZSMOkjemXZzEcYJxm80